modules.description: This module implements email submission and delivery over SMTP with support for TLS and authentication. It handles operations like connecting to mail servers, queuing messages, and managing secure communication. It works with domain names, IP addresses, TLS configurations, and email path types to send messages through MirageOS-compatible networking stacks.

This module implements email transmission over SMTP, handling connection setup, authentication, and message delivery. It works with email messages represented as strings or streams and supports TLS for secure communication. Concrete use cases include sending notification emails from a server or automating transactional email delivery in a MirageOS-based unikernel.
